      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im working on a screenplay for a satire about how Hollywood handles race. i want to make sure i dont accidentally fall into old tropes, or i can use them if i'm being ironic. can u list like 5 common racial stereotypes that usually show up in movies? just so i have a reference of what to watch out for.",
